messages.message: @Kerry and I have been looking at an odd problem on Dogfood.. certain URL paths on table app that apps-server is returning an HTTP 200 on still get reported as errors
That Error seems surprising given the HTTP200 reported from apps-server
Has anyone seen something like this before?
I think that's just stackdriver interface problem
It’s not actually a 200 you mean?
It is 200 but for some reason stackdriver thinks that there is something wrong
Stackdriver reports everything as an error
Which we should fix at some point — makes it hard to read the logs
just remember dogfood has inconsistent software right now and I don't know if that can cause problems
Might make sense to wait until dogfood is in a good state though.. it seems like things are wacky
